race.comment: ATTABOOM (5) showed good early muster and fought on to finish second last start over 1100m at Gunbower. Desperately needs another win but should give a sight. LOU LOU'S CHOICE (6) improved sharply on her seventh two starts back at Mt Gambier with a win over 1100m at Gunbower two weeks ago, her second career victory. May be able to go on with it now. THE MARINER (3) has good speed and will kick up from the inside gate. Chance. From there we move in to the each way chances. SPINHOF (7) has won first up in the past. Holds some value appeal in a thin race. The old boy HAWKESTONE (9) resumed well at Cranbourne. Minor claims.
